  "instructions": [
    "Preheat air fryer to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Place biscuits in a single layer on a baking sheet and bake for 4-5 minutes or until golden brown. Let cool.",
    "Heat peanut oil in a wok over medium heat, add minced onion and bell pepper, sauté until softened.",
    "Add cooled biscuits to the pan, stir-fry for 1 minute, then toss with grated carrot and garlic powder.",
    "Serve hot."
